{"tid":2128443,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"超越Johnson & Johnson  ， Visa 等 台積電成全球市值第十大公司","createTime":"2020-07-28T03:43:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T20:19:20.000Z","uid":28765,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5158055fb7c3ae39f4b13e8a1c2286390732b312","tid":2128443,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T03:43:57.000Z","msg":"台積電股價今（28）日續飆，早盤再度攻上漲停價466.5元，市值持續突破新高；彭博28日報導，台積電股票炙手可熱，股價2天內就上漲720億美元，市值衝破4100億美元，一舉超越嬌生、Visa，成為全球市值第十大公司。<br />\n<br />\n彭博報導，在連日大漲下，台積電市值超過4100億美元，一舉超越美國嬌生和Visa公司，躋身全球市值前十大的公司之1。台積電目前占台股上市比重近3成，近日狂漲更是帶動台股寫下30年來的新高紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3241705\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3241705&d=oFI5KSBgBGvHra6dYUznBhVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=7328ac03\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3241705&h=98b08b20\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3241705</a>"},{"pid":"2aab8b3fe7fbfa807e6897c77ba577cbba3ea892","tid":2128443,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T09:28:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d30eaa8a494b78c52135f22fb83964712a984094","tid":2128443,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T09:53:55.000Z","msg":"想知台仔股十大巨頭仲有啲咩？<br />\n大潤發？"},{"pid":"a72db4ab77120ca4b681bb597118f9865e28c5d6","tid":2128443,"uid":5375,"like":2,"dislike"